# ba5e82dc51d4472e8228372489130589
#: ..\..\Running CMS.rst:55
msgid ""
"At this point, you should have CMS installed on all the machines you want "
"run services on, with the same configuration file, and a running PostgreSQL "
"instance. To run CMS, you need a contest in the database. To create a "
"contest, follow :doc:`these instructions <Creating a contest>`."
