# 4f5fa9f3c51b4e6a92c76d85765590da
#: ..\..\Running CMS.rst:75
msgid ""
"The flag ``-a`` informs ResourceService that it has to start all other "
"services, and we have omitted again the shard number since, even if "
"ResourceService is replicated, there must be only one of it in each machine. "
